Papers!

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.750
Military Governor murdered!

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:04.030
Found brutally killed.

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:05.320
The killer is still at large!

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:07.200
Huge reward for clues!

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:08.960
Extra! Extra!

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:10.120
Military Governor murdered!

00:13:10.510 --> 00:13:11.790
The killer is still at large!

00:13:12.060 --> 00:13:14.500
[Memorial Tablet for Gu Rongchong]

00:13:50.260 --> 00:13:51.900
The Military Governor just passed away.

00:13:52.260 --> 00:13:54.750
The vacancy must be immediately filled.

00:13:55.780 --> 00:13:56.660
Otherwise,

00:13:56.660 --> 00:13:58.340
morale will surely plummet!

00:13:59.420 --> 00:14:00.460
In his lifetime,

00:14:00.740 --> 00:14:02.500
Father favored Tongpei above all.

00:14:03.180 --> 00:14:04.140
Rightfully,

00:14:04.960 --> 00:14:06.500
Tongpei should inherit this position.

00:14:07.380 --> 00:14:07.980
Tongpei,

00:14:08.360 --> 00:14:09.900
you should succeed as Military Governor.

00:14:10.260 --> 00:14:13.460
I vow to uncover the truth
of Father's death.

00:14:15.380 --> 00:14:16.900
Stop playing nice!

00:14:17.480 --> 00:14:18.940
Father's death

00:14:19.100 --> 00:14:20.540
is closely related to you!

00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:22.460
You'll be punished sooner or later!

00:14:23.860 --> 00:14:24.820
And as for you lot,

00:14:25.980 --> 00:14:27.260
my father just passed away,

00:14:28.460 --> 00:14:30.460
yet you rush to install a successor

00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:32.020
to divide the spoils.

00:14:32.460 --> 00:14:34.140
I swear I'll never be your puppet!

